column7: Oh oh oh oh really Sett another offering, for me, why I just don't know what to say, except for: Hooray! And, here, a gift from me!
You got good taste, did I ever tell you? Hehe. And I got good taste too, so I'll be certain to enjoy your little offering, and you go enjoy this!
You want to mess with us?!
Oh hi there, what is new?
You still in one piece, friend?
Sounds good to me there, Sett.
Sure! No, this isn't a prank!
I can't say no to that!
Glad you don't think I'm annoying.
Have I got just the thing for you!
Eh not exactly what I had in mind.
Oh... that's a shame. A big shame.
I have a nasty side too, Sett.
Back off or I'll show you.
Knew you could do it, Sett!
Oh we are going to have a party tonight!
Ooh you're in a real heap of trouble, Sett!
You're ruining the party! We were having such a good time!
My pranks are notorious for a reason, Sett.
